{"tid":2493810,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"漢靈帝算唔算係連登仔最羨慕嘅皇帝？","createTime":"2021-04-18T07:42:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-18T07:51:07.000Z","uid":391580,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fddc562c42231b02ec1e039b4077e08e460c3090","tid":2493810,"uid":391580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T07:42:54.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><strong>光和四年（181年），靈帝在皇宮之中擴建西園，修建集市供自己享樂。靈帝和宮女模仿民間市集裏的商人、竊賊、地痞，並駕着白驢在西園中來回穿梭。甚至起裸游館千間，靈帝特別喜歡嬌嫩純潔的幼女，選十四歲以上十八歲以下的宮女於池中裸游，並命令宮女只能穿開檔褲，原因竟是為了方便自己臨幸宮女。又曾於西園弄狗與人獸交。</strong></span>"},{"pid":"93b121405ebba7ab41adb7908ed550024ad3b497","tid":2493810,"uid":97518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T07:45:15.000Z","msg":"佢下世係拜登定係獵人？"},{"pid":"1c1490572658f291a96cc0e3c03b45aee01cfcc7","tid":2493810,"uid":391580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"93b121405ebba7ab41adb7908ed550024ad3b497","tid":2493810,"uid":97518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T07:45:15.000Z","msg":"佢下世係拜登定係獵人？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T07:48:46.000Z","msg":"14歲以上唔係拜燈啦"},{"pid":"e3488566dc9c28d9920c7a233c279adb43940664","tid":2493810,"uid":393145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"93b121405ebba7ab41adb7908ed550024ad3b497","tid":2493810,"uid":97518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T07:45:15.000Z","msg":"佢下世係拜登定係獵人？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T07:51:07.000Z","msg":"係條開檔褲"}]}